<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<visualNovel>
	<env>
		<title>Opening Day</title>
		<canvas width="30" height="20" fontSize="1.2" saveText="Save Progress" accelText="Skip Text" nextText="==&gt;" />
		<styling>
			<default color="#e4e4e4" bgColor="#101111" linkColor="#234bce" bold="1" italics="0" baseDelay="33" lineDelay="800">
				<delay chars="," time="150" />
				<delay chars=";:" time="300" />
				<delay chars=".!?&#8253;" time="400" />
			</default>
			<class id="ins" baseDelay="0" lineDelay="0">
				<delay chars=",;:.!?&#8253;" time="0" />
			</class>
			<class id="nld" lineDelay="33" />
			<class id="ncd">
				<delay chars=",;:.!?&#8253;" time="33" />
			</class>
			<class id="i" italics="1" />
			<class id="line2x" lineDelay="1600" />
			<class id="john" color="#0715cd" />
			<class id="karkat" color="#626262" />
		</styling>
	</env>
	<flow>
		<block x="1" y="1">
			<text ts-ignore="1">
				<block class="nld">
					<line>#################</line>
					<line>## OPENING DAY ##</line>
					<line>#################</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<line>By Mod E</line>
				<line />
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>To save your progress, click "Save</line>
					<line>Progress" and copy the page's new</line>
					<line>URL somewhere. Use that URL when</line>
					<line>you want to load your game.</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<line class="nld">Click the arrow to begin.</line>
			</text>
			<user />
			<wait>3500</wait>
			<text>
				<block ts-mode="one-line">
					<block class="nld">
						<line>You wake up to the feeling of</line>
						<line>someone shaking your body back-</line>
					</block>
					<line>and-forth.</line>
				</block>
				<line class="ins" />
				<block class="john">
					<line>hey! wake up!</line>
					<line>karkat, it's time to go!</line>
				</block>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text>
				<line>Uuuuurghhhh...</line>
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>Why. Why is this happening to you.</line>
					<line>You were enjoying sleeping! For</line>
					<line>once, you weren't having a</line>
					<line>horrible nightmare from the lack</line>
					<line>of sopor slime. But no. John</line>
					<line><span class="i">fucking</span> Egbert had to come in and</line>
					<line>completely <span class="i">ruin it.</span></line>
				</block>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text class="karkat nld" ts-mode="one-line">
				<line>JOHN, I LOVE YOU, SO I'M GIVING</line>
				<line>YOU A WARNING: LET GO OF ME <span class="i">THIS</span></line>
				<line><span class="i">INSTANT</span> OR YOUR PUNY HUMAN BODY</line>
				<line>WILL BECOME <span class="i">INTIMATELY ACQUAINTED</span></line>
				<line>WITH MY CLAWS. AND BELIEVE ME, IT</line>
				<line>WILL <span class="i">NOT</span> BE PRETTY.</line>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text>
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>Your matesprit, in a rare and</line>
					<line>stunning display of rational</line>
					<line>thinking, abides by your warning</line>
					<line>and removes his mitts from you.</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<block class="nld john" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>karkat, don't you remember what</line>
					<line>today is?</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<block class="nld karkat">
					<line>JOHN. PLEASE. FUCK OFF.</line>
				</block>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text>
				<block class="nld john" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>well fine! i guess i'll just go to</line>
					<line>the <span class="i">grand opening</span> of the new</line>
					<line>cosmagic store without you then!</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<line class="line2x">Wait.</line>
				<line>What did he just say?</line>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text>
				<line class="nld">Ohhh fuck, that's <span class="i">today?</span></line>
				<line />
				<line class="nld">Shit. You need to get moving.</line>
				<line />
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>You quickly pull yourself out of</line>
					<line>bed, throwing the dooner off of</line>
					<line>you. You end up tossing it</line>
					<line>directly at John, which earns you</line>
					<line>some startled noises from him, but</line>
					<line>you're not paying attention. You</line>
					<line>need to <span class="i">get ready.</span></line>
				</block>
			</text>
<!-- max chars per line = 34 -->
<!-- max lines per text block = 12 -->
			<user />
			<text class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
				<line>You quickly rush through your</line>
				<line>routine, putting on your standard</line>
				<line>shirt, sweater, and tracksuit</line>
				<line>pants. You vault down the stairs,</line>
				<line>pulling yourself into the meal</line>
				<line>block and stuffing some nuts down</line>
				<line>your gullet. You grab your phone</line>
				<line>off the counter, stuffing it into</line>
				<line>your right pocket. As you reach</line>
				<line>the door, ready to leave, you spot</line>
				<line>John at the top of the staircase,</line>
				<line>laughing at you.</line>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text>
				<line class="karkat">WHAT? COME ON, WE HAVE TO GO!</line>
				<line class="nld" />
				<block class="nld john" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>hehehe<span class="ncd">.</span>.. karkat, we have, like,</line>
					<line>an hour!</line>
				</block>
				<line class="line2x" />
				<line>What.</line>
				<line class="nld" />
				<block class="nld karkat" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>WHAT&#8253; THEN WHY DID YOU<span class="ncd">..</span>. WHY</line>
					<line>WOULD YOU<span class="ncd">..</span>. RRRRRRRGGGGHHHH...</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>He starts laughing his ass off</line>
					<line>again.</line>
				</block>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text ts-only="1">
				<hr />
			</text>
			<text ts-ignore="1">
				<line>About an hour later...</line>
			</text>
			<user />
			<text>
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
<!--                                          xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx -->
					<line>Still growling at him </line>
				</block>
			</text>
			<user />
			<user />
			<user />
			<user />
			<user />

			<text class="i" ts-ignore="1">
				<line>## END OF DEMO ##</line>
				<line class="nld" />
				<block class="nld" ts-mode="one-line">
					<line>Feel free to give feedback over on</line>
					<line>Discord. UI, color scheme, general</line>
					<line>feel, "this was hard to use on my</line>
					<line>phone"; every piece of feedback is</line>
					<line>welcome.</line>
				</block>
				<line />
				<line>-Mod E</line>
			</text>
		</block>
	</flow>
